
# Azure Node.js App Service Lab

Mini lab Azure démontrant le déploiement d’une application Node.js sur Azure App Service avec CI/CD via GitHub Actions.

---

## Technologies

- Node.js
- Express.js
- Git & GitHub
- GitHub Actions
- Microsoft Azure
- Azure App Service
- Azure CLI
- WSL Ubuntu

---

## Architecture

```text
WSL / VS Code
      ↓
GitHub Repository
      ↓
GitHub Actions CI/CD
      ↓
Azure App Service
      ↓
Node.js Web App
